    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\">\n  <span class=\"breadcrumbs XULRefProp_breadcrumbs\">Â« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL_Reference\" title=\"XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference</a></span></div>\n<dl>\n  <dt>\n    <code><span><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/XUL/Property/smoothScroll\">smoothScroll</a></span></code> </dt>\n  <dd>\n    Type: <em>boolean</em></dd>\n  <dd>\n    Can be set to enable or disable smooth scrolling for the corresponding <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/arrowscrollbox\" title=\"arrowscrollbox\">arrowscrollbox</a></code>. If not set explicitly, it will fall back to the <code id=\"a-smoothscroll\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/smoothscroll\">smoothscroll</a></code> attribute and then to the <code>toolkit.scrollbox.smoothScroll</code> preference. Currently, smooth scrolling supports horizontal arrowscrollboxes only.</dd>\n</dl>",
